OpenTelemetry spans should include trace context propagation for upgradePod (attributes: plan, ordinal, image), exec into containers (for preStop drain), and API server calls. Structured logging with zap fields should include: ts, level, msg, plan, namespace, ordinal, action, duration_ms, error, trace_id, span_id for correlation across logs, metrics, and traces.

